<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">

    <!-- Esercizio 1 -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        <%= numero_esercizio_badge(1) %>
        Leggi, calcola e risolvi.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Colonna sinistra -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Problema A -->
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
              <span class="font-bold">A.</span> Marta sta a scuola 8 ore ogni giorno, dal lunedì al venerdì. Quante ore sta a scuola in una settimana?
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Risposta:</span>
              <input type="text" class="flex-1 min-w-0 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white" placeholder="...">
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Problema B -->
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
              <span class="font-bold">B.</span> Siamo partiti per il mare alle 8:20 del mattino. Abbiamo fatto una sosta di 20 minuti. Siamo arrivati al mare alle 10:20. Quanto è durato il viaggio?
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Risposta:</span>
              <input type="text" class="flex-1 min-w-0 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white" placeholder="...">
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Problema C -->
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
              <span class="font-bold">C.</span> Avevo un appuntamento per le 13:20, ma arriverò con 50 minuti di ritardo. A che ora arriverò?
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Risposta:</span>
              <input type="text" class="flex-1 min-w-0 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white" placeholder="...">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Colonna destra -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Problema D -->
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
              <span class="font-bold">D.</span> Il treno proveniente da Torino doveva arrivare alle 16:55 ma subirà un ritardo di 15 minuti. A che ora arriverà?
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Risposta:</span>
              <input type="text" class="flex-1 min-w-0 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white" placeholder="...">
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Problema E -->
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
              <span class="font-bold">E.</span> Di solito mi alzo alle 7:10, ma domattina devo alzarmi 1 ora e 15 minuti prima del solito. A che ora dovrò alzarmi domani?
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Risposta:</span>
              <input type="text" class="flex-1 min-w-0 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white" placeholder="...">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Spiega come hai ragionato per risolvere questo problema.</p>
            <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white" placeholder="...">
            <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white" placeholder="...">
            <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white" placeholder="...">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Esercizio 2 -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        <%= numero_esercizio_badge(2) %>
        Leggi, rispondi e completa.
      </p>

      <div class="p-3 bg-custom-blue-light dark:bg-cyan-900 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        <p>Marco ha avuto in regalo un orologio con il contasecondi e lo ha utilizzato per controllare il tempo che impiega per fare il giro del quartiere in bicicletta.</p>
        <p>Anche Andrea, Luca e Gianni hanno registrato i loro tempi per il percorso in bicicletta.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="border-collapse border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 text-center">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-100 dark:bg-cyan-800 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Bambino</th>
                <th class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-cyan-100 dark:bg-cyan-800 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Tempi</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Marco</td>
                <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">5 min 58 s</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Andrea</td>
                <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">6 min 30 s</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Luca</td>
                <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">6 min 16 s</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Gianni</td>
                <td class="p-2 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">5 min 38 s</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span>
            <span>Chi ha coperto il tragitto nel minor tempo?</span>
            <input type="text" class="flex-1 min-w-0 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white" placeholder="...">
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span>
            <span>Chi è stato il meno veloce?</span>
            <input type="text" class="flex-1 min-w-0 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white" placeholder="...">
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span>
            <span>Quanti secondi più di Marco ha impiegato Andrea?</span>
            <input type="text" class="flex-1 min-w-0 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white" placeholder="...">
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-cyan-500">•</span>
            <span>Quanti secondi meno di Andrea ha impiegato Luca?</span>
            <input type="text" class="flex-1 min-w-0 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white" placeholder="...">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
